- Created StructuredData component (JSON-LD FinancialService schema) for Google rich results
- Added GA4 analytics placeholder driven by NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID env var
- Fixed footer copyright to fallback to "Requity Group" when company_name is empty in Supabase
- Fixed mobile nav overlay to use full-screen fixed positioning instead of absolute dropdown

